sub_title: PhD Candidate | Utrecht University | LettuceKnow program
summary:
PhD Candidate carrying out research that aims to further the understanding of plant development plasticity in Lettuce. 
My research interests lie in the fields of Plant Developmental Biology, Chemical Ecology and Plant-Microbe interactions.
